text: "Evidence" is a 1995 song by Faith No More. It is the third single from their fifth studio album King for a Day... Fool for a Lifetime. It went to number 32 in the United Kingdom, number 31 in Scotland, number 42 in the Netherlands, number 27 in Australia, number 38 in New Zealand and did not fare well in the United States. ==Track list== ==References== Category:1995 songs Category:Jazz rock songs Category:Faith No More songs
title: Evidence (Faith No More song)
